<p>
The hourly outputs of the WMS at 25 km horizontal intervals in the study domain are used to calculate the generalized wind climate statistics. This was performed using the Danish Technical University (DTU) Generalized Wind Climate software package. The label of each LIB file gives the latitude and longitude (WGS84 datum) location of the 5 km resolution grid cell result which was used to generate the LIB file, as outlined in the example below.

<em>Australia_5km_9.856S_142.310E.lib</em>

